  "What is compound interest?": "什么是复利?",
  "Interest calculated only on the original principal": "仅按原始本金计算的利息",
  "A flat fee charged for borrowing money": "为借款收取的固定费用",
  "The same as simple interest": "与简单利息相同",
  "Interest calculated on the principal plus all previously accumulated interest": "计算本本本加所有先前累计利息的利息",
  "Compound interest is interest calculated on both the initial principal and the interest that has already been added. This means you earn 'interest on interest,' which causes the balance to grow exponentially over time.": "复利是指根据初始本金和已经添加的利息计算的利息。这意味着你赚取“利息利息 ” , 从而导致余额随着时间推移成指数增长。",
  "What is principal?": "校长是什么?",
  "The compounding frequency": "复合频率",
  "The interest rate charged on a loan": "贷款利率",
  "The total amount owed at the end": "截至年底的欠款总额",
  "The original amount of money invested or borrowed before interest": "利息前投资或借款的原始金额",
  "The principal is the initial amount of money that is invested, deposited, or borrowed. It is the starting point for all interest calculations, represented by P in the formulas.": "本金是投资、存款或借款的初始金额,是计算所有利息的起点,在公式中由P表示。",
  "What does 'compounding frequency' mean?": "\"超频\"是什么意思?",
  "How many years the investment lasts": "投资持续了多少年",
  "The total number of interest payments": "支付利息的总额",
  "How large the interest rate is": "利率有多大",
  "How often interest is calculated and added to the principal within a year": "利息在一年内计算并计入本金的频率",
  "Compounding frequency is how many times per year the interest is computed and added to the account balance. Common frequencies include annually (1), semi-annually (2), quarterly (4), monthly (12), and daily (365).": "复计频率是每年计算利息并计入账户余额的次数,共同频率包括每年(1)次,半年(2)次,季度(4)次,每月(12次)和每日(365次)。",
  "What is the Annual Percentage Yield (APY)?": "年产量百分比(APY)是多少?",
  "The principal amount": "本金金额",
  "The effective annual rate that accounts for the effect of compounding": "计算复合效应的有效年利率",
  "The total interest earned over all years": "历年所得利息总额",
  "The nominal interest rate before compounding": "复合之前的名义利率",
  "APY is the effective annual rate of return that accounts for compounding. It is always equal to or greater than the stated (nominal) rate, and it allows for fair comparison between accounts with different compounding frequencies.": "APY是计算化合物的有效年回报率,总等于或大于规定的(名义)回报率,并且可以对不同复合频率的账户进行公平的比较。",
  "What is the Rule of 72?": "什么是72规则?",
  "A rule stating interest rates cannot exceed 72%": "规定利率不得超过72%的规则",
  "A formula for computing monthly payments": "计算月支付额的公式",
  "A law about maximum loan amounts": "关于最高贷款额的法律",
  "A quick estimation that money doubles in approximately 72 divided by the interest rate (as a percent) years": "快速估计货币在大约72年中翻一番,除以利率(百分比),再除以年利率(百分比)",
  "The Rule of 72 estimates the doubling time of an investment: years to double ≈ 72 / (interest rate in percent). For example, at 6% interest, money doubles in about 72/6 = 12 years.": "72 规则估计了投资的翻一番时间:年数翻一番 72 /(利率为% ) 。 例如,利率为6%,在大约72/6年中货币翻一番 = 12 年。",
  "What is simple interest?": "什么是简单的利益?",
  "Interest that changes rate each year": "每年利率变化的利息",
  "Interest computed on both principal and accumulated interest": "以本本金和累计利息计算的利息",
  "Interest computed only on the original principal, using I = Prt": "利息仅按原本金计算,使用 I = Prt",
  "Interest that compounds continuously": "连续化合物的利息",
  "Simple interest is calculated only on the original principal amount, not on any accumulated interest. The formula I = Prt gives the total interest earned, where P is principal, r is rate, and t is time.": "简单利息仅根据原始本金数额计算,而不是根据任何累计利息计算。公式I = Prt给出所得利息总额,P为本金,r为利率,t为时间。",
  "What does 'continuous compounding' mean?": "\"连续复合\"是什么意思?",
  "Compounding 365 times per year": "每年复置365次",
  "Compounding once per year": "每年复合一次",
